00:13:06,911 --> 00:13:09,538
Just two more minutes.
No more antique shops.

191
00:13:15,253 --> 00:13:18,088
Mm, thank you. Put that down.

192
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,008
Rory.
[IN OLD MAN'S VOICE] Klondike 474.

193
00:13:21,176 --> 00:13:23,385
Repeat 47...

