You love words.

875
01:10:16,421 --> 01:10:21,675
I'm young, spoiled, impetuous
and American. Humor me.

876
01:10:23,761 --> 01:10:27,806
Please? Pretty, pretty, pretty please?

877
01:10:28,016 --> 01:10:30,225
